    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Make a single attack with your held projectile weapon. If the attack hits, it deals 1d6 bonus piercing damage. A Samurai with at least 6 class levels may substitute this technique for a normal attack when they make a Full Attack (using the same attack bonus as the substituted attack), but only if they chose the Kyujutsu path. If you substitute the technique this way, it cannot be empowered and the Perform Requirements are automatically met.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the bonus damage by 1d6, up to 1d6 per 2 levels or 6d6 total.</p>\n\n",
